    "title": "Marketplace Manager - FabAlley South Asia Partners - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at FabAlley South Asia Partners. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Kochi-based team.\n\nAbout FabAlley South Asia Partners:\nFabAlley South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FabAlley South Asia Partners!",
